      • ProtoConverter

        public ProtoConverter(boolean validateColPosition)
        Instantiate a {ProtoConverter} using a typeMap.
        Parameters:
        validateColPosition - whether to consider column position in this converter. By default, a {TiDAGRequest} should check whether a {ColumnRef}'s position is correct in it's executors. Can ignore this validation if `validateColPosition` is set to false.
